platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Bizarre doesn’t even begin to explain Young Horses’ laugh-out-loud game. You control a father who’s secretly an octopus, and moving the bendy protagonist around makes for hysterically madcap fun. You’ll slip, slap, and slide your way through stages stacked with objects for you to interact with—mostly by crashing into them. Octodad’s hilariously animated chaos is wacky and simply irresistible.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: Get married, raise some kids - but don't give away that you're an octopus.
タコが一人の父親として家族と暮らす、一風変わったシミュレーションゲーム。
Pas toujours simple la vie de père... surtout pour une pieuvre !
